      "text": "Wonderful to be at the York and Seward/Milford rest areas to celebrate the 50th anniversary of the I-80 sculpture project. This project used a 455-mile transportation corridor as a canvas for works of limestone, aluminum, steel, and granite in a lasting tribute to our https://t.co/niG1K5If9d",
