      "profileHref": "/country/usa/congress/deb-fischer",
      "text": "To celebrate America’s 250th birthday, I attended the Great American State Fair with Team Fischer. I especially enjoyed stamping my passport at the Nebraska pavilion. I am glad visitors from across the country got a taste of the Good Life in our nation’s capital! https://t.co/3izoKkzaKc",
